0.2.0
- feat: optional pyFFTW backend for faster CPU Fourier transforms
  (install with `pip install xpunwrap[FFTW]`); selected automatically on the
  numpy backend, with numpy FFT as fallback and cupy FFT on the GPU backend
- fix: package `xpunwrap.algorithms` (and new `xpunwrap.fourier`) in built
  wheels via setuptools package discovery

